Package: monochromeR
Title: Easily Create, View and Use Monochrome Colour Palettes
Version: 0.2.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person(
    "Cara",
    "Thompson",
    role = c("aut", "cre"),
    email = "packages@cararthompson.com",
    comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-6472-5073")
    )
Description: Let's you create and view monochrome colour palettes. Two options
    are given to create palettes, go towards black and white from your start
    colour or "blend" your start colour with another colour.
